            <Heading tagName="h2" size="h2">ðŸ‘‹ Hey, Iâ€™m Katie</Heading>
            <p>I like to write about productivity, web development, design, and working with clients. Get a sense of what itâ€™s like to work with me and understand my process.</p>
        </div>
    </section>
</BaseLayout>